Interface ISemanticsAware

All Superinterfaces:
ISelectable
All Known Implementing Classes:
Axon, BrainRegion, CCDBSlide, ContainerTangible, Curve3D, CurveAnchorPoint, DataMesh, Layer, NeurolucidaNeuronMorphology, NeuroMLNetwork, NeuronCable, NeuronMorphology, NeuronSegment, Slide, SphereParticles, Surface, Tangible, TiledSlide, Volume
public interface ISemanticsAware
extends ISelectable

Any type that needs to be associated with a list of ISemanticThings and have those ISemanticThings be associated with it.

Stephen D. Larson (slarson@ncmir.ucsd.edu)
